data.description: Welcome to an amazing home in the sought-after North Rock Creek School district! Nestled on a generous 3/4-acre lot, this stunning residence offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and classic charm. With a spacious garage, a convenient storm cellar, and an array of desirable features, this property is an exceptional find for families and those seeking a serene suburban lifestyle. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting living space that effortlessly combines warmth and functionality. The open floor plan provides a seamless flow from room to room, making this home ideal for both everyday living and entertaining. The home boasts three well-appointed bedrooms, offering plenty of space for a growing family or guests. The primary suite is a tranquil retreat with ample closet space and a private ensuite bathroom with separated soaking tub and shower. Upstairs, you'll find a versatile bonus room that can be used as a playroom, movie room or home office, providing additional living space for your family's needs. The kitchen features gleaming granite countertops, modern stainless steel appliance, spacious pantry and room for a breakfast bar. Whether you're preparing family meals or hosting dinner parties, this kitchen is sure to impress. The backyard offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply relaxing on the patio with a cup of coffee in the mornings. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful property your forever home. All of this on paved roads with rural water, natural gas, and fiber optic high speed internet! Schedule a showing today to experience the lifestyle this property has to offer!
